{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"- (","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removePack:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)MLNOfflinePack","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","text":"MLNOfflinePack","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"pack","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"withCompletionHandler:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:MLNOfflineStorage.h@T@MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler","text":"MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"completion","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The offline pack to remove.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"pack"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The completion handler to call once the pack has been"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"removed. This handler is executed asynchronously on the main queue."}]}],"name":"completion"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"As soon as this method is called on a pack, the pack becomes invalid; any"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"attempt to send it a message will result in an exception being thrown. If an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"error occurs and the pack cannot be removed, do not attempt to reuse the pack"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object. Instead, if you need continued access to the pack, suspend all packs"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and use the "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage\/reloadPacks","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" method to obtain valid pointers to all the packs."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To detect when any call to this method results in a pack being removed, observe"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"KVO change notifications on the shared offline storage object’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"packs"},{"type":"text","text":" key"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"path. Removals from that array result in an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSKeyValueChangeRemoval"},{"type":"text","text":" change."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"When you remove an offline pack, any resources that are required by that pack,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"but not other packs, become eligible for deletion from offline storage. Because","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the backing store used for offline storage is also used as a general purpose","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"cache for map resources, such resources may not be immediately removed if the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"implementation determines that they remain useful for general performance of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the map.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage\/removePack:withCompletionHandler:"},"sections":[],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Instance Method","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removePack:withCompletionHandler:","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","title":"removePack:withCompletionHandler:","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNOfflineStorage(im)removePack:withCompletionHandler:","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"removePack:withCompletionHandler:"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"symbolKind":"method"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage\/removepack:withcompletionhandler:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"abstract":[{"text":"Unregisters the given offline pack and allows resources that are no longer","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"required by any remaining packs to be potentially freed.","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage"]]},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflineStorage":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage","title":"MLNOfflineStorage","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage","abstract":[{"text":"MLNOfflineStorage implements a singleton (shared object) that manages offline","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"packs and ambient caching. All of this class’s instance methods are asynchronous,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"reflecting the fact that offline resources are stored in a database. The shared","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"object maintains a canonical collection of offline packs in its ","type":"text"},{"code":"packs","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" property.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNOfflineStorage","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePack":{"role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" represents a collection of resources necessary for viewing"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a region offline to a local database."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNOfflinePack","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepack","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNOfflinePack"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler":{"title":"MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler","abstract":[{"text":"A block to be called once an offline pack has been completely invalidated and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"removed.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinepackremovalcompletionhandler","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler","role":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"MLNOfflinePackRemovalCompletionHandler","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflineStorage/reloadPacks":{"title":"reloadPacks","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Forcibly, asynchronously reloads the "},{"code":"packs","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property. At some point after this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method is called, the pointer values of the "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflinePack","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" objects in the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"packs","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property change, even if the underlying data for these packs has not"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"changed. If this method is called while a pack is actively downloading, the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"behavior is undefined."}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage\/reloadpacks","type":"topic","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"reloadPacks"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"reloadPacks"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage\/reloadPacks"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","role":"collection","title":"MapLibre","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOfflineStorage/removePack:withCompletionHandler:":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage\/removepack:withcompletionhandler:","role":"symbol","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"removePack:withCompletionHandler:","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Unregisters the given offline pack and allows resources that are no longer"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"required by any remaining packs to be potentially freed."}],"kind":"symbol","title":"removePack:withCompletionHandler:","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"removePack:withCompletionHandler:","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage\/removePack:withCompletionHandler:"}}}